snippet.title: Path of War: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Path of War is a MMO combat strategy game available for iOS and Android devices. Design your headquarters, raise a fearsome army and wreak a path of destruction across the United States in 1-to-1 scale! 

United we will Conquer!

PLAY NOW FOR FREE: 
iOS: http://apple.co/1PIWZkp
Android: http://bit.ly/1PIkJFl

Website: http://pathofwargame.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pathofwar/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/pathofwar
